        {
            "title": "山東黃金去年盈利升28%",
            "description": "<p>山東黃金(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/01787' >01787</a>)公布截至2024年12月底止年度業績，股東應佔利潤28.99億元(人民幣．下同)，按年增長27.84%，每股盈利0.56元，派末期息每10股1.48元。</p>\n<p>期內，收入825.18億元，按年升39.21%。</p>\n<p>集團表示，當前，在全球政治經濟形勢不確定性更加突出的背景下，黃金需求有望繼續保持旺盛；預計黃金在全球資產配置中的保值功能和避險價值將會進一步提升，黃金行業面臨着較好的發展機遇。<span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">公</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">司</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">將</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">充</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">分</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">發</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">揮</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">大</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">型</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">黃</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">金</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">企</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">龍</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">頭</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">帶</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">動</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">作</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">用，</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">統</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">籌</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">布</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">局</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">國</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">內</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">與</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">國</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">際</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">市</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">場，依</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">託</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">重</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">要</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">成</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">礦</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">帶</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">資</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">源</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">整</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">合</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">優</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">勢，穩</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">步</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">推</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">進</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">對</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">國</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">內</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">外</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">優</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">質</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">資</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">源</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">併</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">購，確</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">保</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">重</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">點</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">區</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">域</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">整</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">體</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">產</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">能</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">快</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">速</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">高</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">效</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">釋</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">放。同</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">時，加</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">快</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">基</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">建</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">礦</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">山</span><s